Class PayrollProcessing

java.lang.Object
PayrollProcessing
public class PayrollProcessing
extends java.lang.Object
A class that facilitates the input and output of the program -- The User Interface. This simulates a company's payroll.
Author:
Abdullah Salem, Gent Blaku
